{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.680", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.480", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.120", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.200", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kollege Reichardt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.520", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre kruden Thesen und fremdenfeindlichen Parolen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.000", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie hier wirklich bei jedem Tagesordnungspunkt irgendwo anbringen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.040", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden tats\u00e4chlich nicht besser, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.520", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie hier am fr\u00fchen Morgen so herumschreien. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.760", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das macht es kein bisschen besser."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.600", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.400", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gute und erfolgreiche Familienpolitik muss mit dem rasanten Wandel in der Gesellschaft Schritt halten und ihm gerecht werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.440", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frauen wollen heute eben nicht mehr nur Mutter sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.680", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern sie wollen auch im Beruf erfolgreich sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.600", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und V\u00e4ter wollen nicht mehr auf die Rolle des Ern\u00e4hrers reduziert werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.480", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern aktiv an der Erziehung ihrer Kinder teilhaben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.880", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Elterngeld mit seinen Weiterentwicklungen Elterngeld Plus und Partnerschaftsbonus kann dabei unterst\u00fctzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.200", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie der vorliegende Bericht an einigen Stellen auch zeigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.720", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beide Weiterentwicklungen erm\u00f6glichen jedenfalls im Grundsatz mehr Flexibilit\u00e4t und eine verbesserte partnerschaftliche Vereinbarkeit von Familie und Beruf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.800", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist auch gut so."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.960", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leider l\u00e4sst der Bericht wichtige Fragen aber offen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.440", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und er betreibt damit ganz bewusst Sch\u00f6nf\u00e4rberei. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.040", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.840", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Ministerin Barley, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.040", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wirklich h\u00e4tten wissen wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.200", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es um das Elterngeld Plus steht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.680", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann h\u00e4tten Sie doch nicht nur diejenigen befragt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.120", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die es beziehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.400", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich also ganz bewusst f\u00fcr diese Leistung entschieden haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.120", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zumal das auch gerade einmal nur 28\u00a0Prozent der Anspruchsberechtigten waren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.320", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viel spannender ist doch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.280", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was mit den \u00fcbrigen 72\u00a0Prozent ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.280", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zwar Elterngeld beziehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich aber offenbar gegen das Elterngeld\u00a0Plus entschieden haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.920", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die kommen in Ihrem Bericht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.440", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der sich ja auf eine Befragung von knapp 1\u00a0000\u00a0Personen st\u00fctzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.320", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcberhaupt nicht zu Wort."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.040", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei k\u00f6nnte doch nur diese Gruppe die entscheidende Frage beantworten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.240", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum sich so viele gegen das Elterngeld Plus entscheiden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.280", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Frage zu stellen und in Ihrem Bericht zu beantworten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.400", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4re methodisch sauberer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.920", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erkenntnisreicher und auch ehrlicher gewesen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.040", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bleibt also, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.320", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "uns mit den abgefragten Informationen auseinanderzusetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.520", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese offenbaren ein sehr differenziertes Bild. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.480", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Zahlen zeigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.400", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Bundesregierung das wesentliche Ziel bei der Einf\u00fchrung von Elterngeld Plus und Partnerschaftsbonus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.800", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also die Vereinbarkeit von Familie und Beruf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.040", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei einer gro\u00dfen Gruppe der Familien schlicht verfehlt hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.640", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jede f\u00fcnfte Frau gibt an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.320", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aufgrund des Elterngeldes Plus l\u00e4ngere Zeit aus dem Beruf ausgestiegen zu sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.920", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "M\u00fctter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.600", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Elterngeld\u00a0Plus mehr als 20\u00a0Monate beziehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.720", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gehen nur sehr selten einer Erwerbst\u00e4tigkeit nach; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.400", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "genauso wenig nutzen ihre Familien den Partnerschaftsbonus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.960", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie teilen also Job und Kindererziehung kaum."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.560", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gut funktionieren Elterngeld Plus und Partnerschaftsbonus vor allem f\u00fcr doppelverdienende Paare mit \u00e4hnlich hohem Einkommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.280", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da bewirken sie tats\u00e4chlich eine Flexibilisierung der Arbeitszeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.600", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verdienen Eltern dagegen sehr unterschiedlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.200", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist eine Berufst\u00e4tigkeit f\u00fcr den Geringerverdienenden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.040", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meistens ist es ja die Frau\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.840", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenig attraktiv. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.720", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit erreicht das Elterngeld Plus f\u00fcr viele Paare eben keine bessere Vereinbarkeit von Familie und Beruf und auch keine verbesserte partnerschaftliche Aufgabenteilung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.000", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern genau das Gegenteil, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.520", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich den Ausstieg aus dem Beruf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.520", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kollegin Sch\u00f6n, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.360", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deshalb k\u00f6nnen wir in die Lobeshymnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.320", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie angestimmt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.400", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht einsteigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.920", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch heute nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.320", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.040", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir lernen aus dem Bericht: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.720", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Elterngeld Plus setzt widerspr\u00fcchliche Anreize. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.560", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das gilt auch f\u00fcr die deutsche Familienpolitik insgesamt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.880", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber die Jahrzehnte kamen zahllose familienpolitische Ma\u00dfnahmen dazu. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.280", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alte Leistungen wurden aber nicht gestrichen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.920", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aktuell sind es \u00fcber 150\u00a0Leistungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.520", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich in ihren Zielen zum Teil erheblich widersprechen und damit gegenseitig blockieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.240", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass die neue zuk\u00fcnftige GroKo jetzt viele weitere angek\u00fcndigt hat,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.880", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne eine fundierte Evaluation der bestehenden Leistungen vorzunehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.640", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist nicht automatisch ein Grund zur Freude, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.000", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.960", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fast 200\u00a0Milliarden\u00a0Euro\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.400", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sind nahezu zwei Drittel des Haushaltes\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.720", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "flie\u00dfen jedes Jahr in die Familienpolitik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.440", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Trotzdem werden die Familien nicht passgenau unterst\u00fctzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.160", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das darf auf gar keinen Fall so bleiben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.040", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Steuerzahler und Familien haben ein Recht darauf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.840", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Mittel wirksamer investiert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
